Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.26,0:03:33.62,cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz19.851\fn仿宋\b0\pos(371,305)}替補隊員的強化
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.26,0:03:33.62,cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn仿宋\b0\fs40\pos(566,374)\frz14.982}體力提升
